            . I apprehended the prisoner, I asked him about Miles's pig; he told us where it was and there we found it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. Mr. Mole told me if I would tell him where to find it, he would think no more about it; I gave him the money I had left of the price of the pig, three pounds seven shillings and three pence halfpenny.</p>
